Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus (COVID-19) wiyongereye cyane mu Burayi / mu karere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi no mu Bwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abandura indwara ya Coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza imiterere imwe mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, byemeza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu byose, nubwo kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye bitewe n'ibihugu.
Dushingiye ku bumenyi bwavuye mu Butaliyani, igihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi byihuse, cyane cyane mu byiciro by'ubuvuzi bukomeye, bigomba kongera imyiteguro.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, hagezweho icyorezo cya pneumonia cyatewe n'ibitekerezo by'abantu bataramenyekana.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko Coronavirus nshya ari yo ifite ubushobozi bwo gukora, kuva ubu ikaba yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ku bw'ibyo, uburwayi buturuka ku kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bwiswe indwara ya Koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, amakuru yemewe ni uko 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bworoheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bufite cyangwa budafite pneumonia, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu 14% banduye, COVID-19 iba icyorezo gikomeye cyane gisaba kuvurirwa mu bitaro, naho 6% bagerwaho n'uburwayi bukomeye cyane bukenera kwitabwaho cyane.
Imibare y'abapfuye mu bitaro bishwe na COVID-19 ni hafi 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye imiterere y'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza, tukayigereranya n'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone kandi, twahuriye imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'iy'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibibazo bya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
COVID-19 ikwirakwira cyane mu karere gakurikiye Ubushinwa, kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bice byose by'isi ubu gikurikirana iki gihugu.
COVID-19 yashyizwe ku mugaragaro n'Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Mu kinyamakuru cyitwa Eurosurveillance 2020, cyo ku wa 5 Werurwe, Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje ko ari bo bantu ba mbere b'i Burayi bemeje COVID-19 nk'uko bitangazwa na OMS.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe n'Ubufaransa ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 yari imaze kugaragara mu bihugu byose 30 bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, aho abarwayi 39,768 n'abapfuye 1,727 batangajwe kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu gihe mu Butaliyani honyine habonetse abarwayi 17,750 n'abapfuye 1,441.
