Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) cyatangaza imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 ku isi yose, mu bihugu byose, gusa ibikuwe mu minisiteri y'ubuzima y'ibihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'akarere, n'ibikoresho bya leta nka OMS, bigahora bishyirwa ahagaragara saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza no kugereranya n'ibyabaye mu Butaliyani.
Nk'igihereranyo cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje, twakoze imibare y'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu minsi 14, dutekereza ku buryo COVID-19 yagendaga muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza kuva ku wa 1 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twatanze imibare y'ubwandu buri gihugu cyabonye guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'amanywa, tugereranyije n'ubwandu bwo mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
