Birashoboka ko inyamaswa nyinshi zinyamaswa, harimo n'iz'ingurube, zishobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku binyabuzima byo mu ngo no mu ishyamba bwemeje ko hari udukoko twanduza indwara.
Icya gatatu, nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, gusubirana no guhinduranya SARS-CoV-2 bishobora kuba byarabaye mu bwoko bwa gatatu bufite imikorobe n'ibinyamushongo.
Gushakisha inkomoko y'inyamaswa ya SARS-CoV-2 biracyakomeje.
