CoV-series ifite exoribonuclease isoma, iseswa ryayo rishobora gutuma ihinduka cyane kandi ikagira intege nke cyangwa se idashobora kubaho.
Igishishikaje ni uko iyi exoribonuclease na RNA-dependent RNA polymerases ya Remdesivir, ingira uruhare mu gutuma habaho imikorere ya CoV.
Remdesivir ni kimwe mu bintu bishobora kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 byatangiye kugeragezwa mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi.
Nyamara, umubare w'abandura muri CoV-s uri hejuru cyane inshuro zigera kuri miliyoni ugereranyije n'abari mu ngo zabo.
Byongeye kandi, igihe CoV zitagendana n'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima, akenshi usanga zigira igipimo cyo hejuru cy'imiterere.
Ugereranyije na SARS-CoV ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cy'ubwiyongere, SARS-CoV-2 ifite igipimo cyo hasi cyo guhinduka, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko abantu bashobora guhinduka mu buryo bworoshye.
Birashoboka ko byamaze kumenyerana n'undi muntu uri hafi.
Uretse SARS-CoV-2, ni na ko bimeze kuri MERS-CoV, ikunda guhuza neza n'ingamiya ifite imishishi.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, nta gushidikanya ko imiterere y'imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gutuma inkingo n'imiti ya antiviral bitagira ingaruka vuba.
