Amateka y'indwara: (1) kuba umuturage cyangwa se kuba yaragiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu nkengero zawo, cyangwa se mu yindi midugudu aho havuzwe ko hari abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara; (2) kuba yaragiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa mu nkengero zawo, cyangwa se mu yindi midugudu aho havuzwe ko hari abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara; (2) kuba yaragiye mu miryango y'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 (yagize umusaruro mwiza mu gupima aside ya nikeleyeri); (3) kuba yaragiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa mu nkengero zawo, cyangwa se mu yindi midugudu aho havuzwe ko hari abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara; (4) kuba yaragiye mu miryango yemeza ko hari abantu banduye COVID-19 (mu byumweru 2 cyangwa birenze, mu duce duto cyane nko mu ngo, mu biro, mu mashuri, n'ibindi, kandi afite umuriro/indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ≥ 2 kg).
Ibimenyetso by'ubushakashatsi: (1) ubushyuhe n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) ibimenyetso byerekana ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) imibare yose y'amaraso yera mu gihe cy'ubwandu bw'ibanze, igaragaza imibare isanzwe, yagabanutse cyangwa yagabanutse ya limfocyte.
Kugira ngo umuntu asuzumwe asuzumwe, hagomba kuba hari kimwe mu bimenyetso bikurikira: (1) kuba umuntu yitabye SARS-CoV-2 mu gihe cy'ubushakashatsi bwa PCR; (2) kuba afite homogenite cyangwa ihurizo ryinshi na virusi nshya ya coronavirus izwi mu buryo bwuzuye mu buryo bw'imiterere ya virusi; (3) kuba umuntu yitabye SARS-CoV-2 mu gihe cy'ibipimo bya serum byerekana IgM na IgG; cyangwa kuba umuntu yitabye SARS-CoV-2 mu gihe cy'ibipimo by'imiterere byerekana ko IgG ari ingenzi kurusha ingufu z'ubushakashatsi bwagaragaye mu gihe cy'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe.
