Iki gikorwa cy'ingenzi cyabaye ku munsi Malawi yemejeho icyorezo cya mbere cya Coronavirus ndetse n'urupfu rwa mbere rufitanye isano na Coronavirus muri Zambia.
Kugeza ku wa kane, Koreya ya Ruguru yari yavuze ko ari kimwe mu bihugu bike bisigaye bitanduye coronavirus.
Kugeza ejo, OMS yari imaze kwandika abantu 1,051,635 banduye, harimo 79,332 mu masaha 24 ashize, saa kumi za mu gitondo ku itariki ya 4 Mata, igihe cy'i Burayi bwo hagati (0800 UTC).
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, hamaze kwandura coronavirus irenga 244.000, ihitana abantu bagera kuri 5,900.
CBS News ikoresha amakuru ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins ivuga ko abantu barenga 1000 muri Amerika bishwe n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus kuri uyu wa gatatu.
Ku isi hose, ibihugu byatangaje ko bigiye gufata ingamba zikomeye zo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
Ku wa kane, Mayor wa Moscow, Sergei Sobyanin, yongeyeho igihe cyo gufunga umujyi kugeza ku wa 1 Gicurasi.
Ku rwego rw'igihugu, Perezida Vladimir Putin yatangaje ko amafaranga azakomeza gutangwa nubwo Abarusiya batazajya ku kazi kugeza ku itariki ya 30 Mata.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Portugal yemeye ko itegeko ry'ubutegetsi bw'ikirenga ryongerwaho iminsi 15, ryemezwa n'amajwi 215 y'abashyigikiye, 10 batishimiye, n'umwe warishyigikiye.
Arabiya Sawudite yongereye amasaha yo gutaha mu mujyi mutagatifu wa Maka na Madina, ku munsi wose, kuva saa tatu z'umugoroba kugeza saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo.
Igihugu cya Thailande cyari cyateguye ko habaho amasaha y'ikiruhuko kuva saa kumi z'ijoro kugeza saa yine za mu gitondo.
Guverineri wa Ohio, Mike DeWine yatangaje ko leta yongereye igihe cyo kuguma mu nzu kugeza ku wa 1 Gicurasi.
Ubucuruzi bwo muri Ositaraliya bugabanya umubare w'impapuro z'isuku ku kintu cy'ubucuruzi
Ku cyumweru no ku wa gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya ya Woolworths na Coles yagabanyije ku rwego rw'igihugu imipaka yo kugura impapuro z'isuku ku isoko rimwe mu maduka yose, ku buryo ari bibiri n'ipaki imwe.
Byongeye kandi, mu kwezi kwa cyenda, ALDI yashyizeho imipaka y'ipakete imwe.
Izo mbogamizi zashyizwe ku mbuga nkoranyambaga no ku mbuga nkoranyambaga za Facebook.
Abaguzi bavuga ko batangiye kugura ibintu kubera gutinya COVID-19 mu gihe abantu babaga bagomba kwitandukanya.
Ku wa gatatu, Woolworths na yo yagabanyije igurishwa ry'impapuro z'isuku zo gutumiza mu rugo, igura impapuro imwe ku busabe.
Izi mpinduka zikurikije ibikubiye mu byo bagurishije mbere, kuko Woolworths na Coles batangije amapaji ane ku ya 4 na 5 Werurwe.
"Ku ya 8 Werurwe, ikigo cya Coles cyatangaje ko mu bice bitandukanye hatangiye itegeko ryo guhagarika ibyokurya by'amapaki ane, ariko ko "ibigo byinshi bikomeje kugurisha byose mu gihe cy'isaha imwe", bavuga ko ibyo bakeneye ari "ibitigeze bibaho", ndetse mu butumwa bwo kuri Facebook ku wa kabiri kuri ALDI bavuga ko ari "ibitari byitezwe".
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuvugizi wa Woolworths, mu cyumweru gishize, ubucuruzi bw'ibicuruzwa bwazamutse cyane.
Mu cyumweru gishize, ibicuruzwa by'i Costco muri Canberra byemerewe gutangwa mu ma paketi abiri.
Mu rwego rwo kurushaho kugabanya ibura, Coles yasabye ibicuruzwa byinshi ku babigurisha, kandi yongereraho umubare w'ibikoresho byongera gutangwa, Woolworths yasabye ibicuruzwa by'inyongera, aho ALDI yatumye ibicuruzwa biboneka mbere y'itariki ya gatatu yihariye.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi bo muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa, ariko ko amategeko y'inama y'akarere ku gihe cyo gutanga ibicuruzwa mu magare aribyo bituma bigorana.
Mu gihe abatanga ibicuruzwa bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo, yiteze ko igiciro cy'umusaruro kizamuka.
Ku wa kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko kubera ko hari ibitabo byashize, hari amaduka atari kuzakora ubucuruzi bwihariye ku wa Gatatu.
Mu nkuru ya News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu by'ubucuruzi muri Kaminuza ya Queensland ikora ikoranabuhanga, yavuze ko buri joro amaduka yuzuza ibyangombwa.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'isuku ari ikintu kiremereye cyane ku buryo hari umubare muto w'ibikoresho biboneka, kandi ko iyo byose byagurishijwe, ibitabo byinshi bihinduka ubusa, bigatuma abantu barushaho kumva ko hari ibura.
"Nk'uko ABC News ibivuga, "Coles na Woolworths batekereza ko niba umuntu afite ibintu byinshi, kandi akaba afite ibintu byinshi, nk'udupapuro tw'isuku n'ibisukika, kandi bikaba bihagije, ashobora kugabanya ubwoba bwe", Russell Zimmerman yaravuze.
Ku wa gatatu, ikigo gikora impapuro z'isuku zongera gukoreshwa, Hu Gives a Crap, cyavuze ko igiye kubura.
Nk'uko amakuru yo ku rubuga rwa News.com.au abivuga, Kimberly-Clark, ikora umwenda w'isuku wa Clinex n'impapuro z'ubushyuhe zitunganya umusaruro, yashimangiye ko ikora amasaha 24 kuri 24 kugira ngo ibyangombwa bikomeze gutangwa.
Urubuga rw'ubucuruzi bw'umutungo utimukanwa Domain.com rwatangaje ko hari abacuruzi b'imitungo barimo baha umwenda w'isuku ku buntu abatangaga mbere mu cyamunara i Melbourne, bamwe muri bo bakaba barawutanze kubera ko abaguzi bari bafite ikiruhuko cy'icyumweru kirekire cy'akazi.
Kuri uyu wa kane, ikinyamakuru NT News cyandikwa buri munsi muri Darwin, cyatanze impapuro umunani z'inyandiko zikoreshwa mu gutema ibyo bitabo, zikaba ari impapuro z'isuku.
Raporo ya BBC Australia yo ku wa 3 Werurwe yavuze ko amaduka ahanini yanze gushyiraho ingamba, avuga ko nta gahunda bafite zo gushyiraho ingamba ku by'ubucuruzi.
Russell Zimmerman avuga ko hari ibindi bintu bikenewe cyane, birimo udupfukamunwa, sanitizer, imboga, imyenda yo gukaraba intoki n'ifu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Ositaraliya, buri wa Gatandatu nimugoroba, ku isoko ry'ibanze ry'Abongereza rya Okado, ubucuruzwa bw'impapuro z'isuku za Andres zikoreshwa mu bwiherero, bugabanijwe ku bipfunyika bibiri by'ibitabo 12.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryemeje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 ari icyorezo.
"Nubwo ijambo ""icyorezo"" ridasobanura ko hari abantu bafite uburwayi runaka, ahubwo ko risobanura uburyo indwara runaka yakwirakwiriye, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryagaragaje ko hari hakenewe ko leta zifata ingamba:"
"Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyorezo cyugarije isi".
"Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa WHO Adhanom Ghebreyesus yavuze ko niba ibihugu bishobora kumenya, "" gupima, kuvura, gutandukanya, kumenya no guhuza. ""
"Turahangayitse cyane kubera ikwirakwira ry'indwara ndetse n'ibipimo by'ubukana n'ubushomeri biteye ubwoba".
"Dogoteri Tom Friedan, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Gukumira no Kurinda Indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo cyugarije isi ari "ikintu kitigeze kibaho".
Mu magambo yatangarije CNN muri Gashyantare, yagize ati "Nta virusi yindi y'ubuhumekero, uretse influenza, yagaragaye mu gihe cy'ubwandu bukomeje gukwirakwira ku isi".
Gabrussas na we yavuze ko "nta cyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus twigeze tubona".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi ntitwigeze tubona icyorezo cy'isi yose gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
Iyi ndwara ya COVID-19 imaze iminsi ivugwa mu Rwanda, mu Rwanda no mu bindi bihugu, ariko ubu iracyari mu bihugu bikennye.
Dr Anthony Fauci, umuyobozi w'ikigo cy'igihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe indwara zandura n'indwara z'uburwayi, yavuze kuri iki cyorezo ati "mu by'ukuri, ibintu biragenda birushaho kuba bibi".
Associated Press yatangaje kuri uyu wa Kane ko ku isi hose, umubare w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 ari 126,000, aho abantu barenga 4,600 bapfuye.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20 ni icyorezo cya Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze cyane yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangajwe ko ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'abaturage gihangayikishije Isi yose ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama 2020, ndetse cyemezwa ko ari icyorezo ku isi hose ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, hamaze kuboneka abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere tw'ubumwe bw'Amerika, aho hamaze gupfa abantu bagera ku 97,000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 bamaze gukira.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa ugereranywa na 4%, mu gihe ku isi hose, uhereye kuri 13.04% muri Algeria ukagera kuri 0.08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe ni umuriro, gucumba no guhumeka nabi.
Ibibazo bishobora kuba birimo uburwayi bwa pimoine n'indwara y'umuvuduko mwinshi wo guhumeka.
Igihe cyo guhura n'umuntu kugeza igihe ibimenyetso bitangirira, akenshi kiba ari iminsi itanu, ariko gishobora kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza ku minsi 14.
Nta rukingo cyangwa imiti yihariye ya virusi.
Ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ni ubufasha bwo kuvura no gufasha. Ingamba zo kwirinda zisabwa harimo gukaraba intoki, gutwikira mu maso mu gihe ukorora, kwirinda abandi bantu, no kugenzura no kwigunga abantu bakekwaho kuba banduye.
Abategetsi ku isi hose bitabiriye ibyo bikorwa bashyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda ingendo, gushyira abantu mu kato, gufunga imiryango, kugabanya ibyago byo mu kazi no guhagarika ibikorwa.
Icyorezo cyibasiye isi cyateje ihungabana rikomeye ry'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abantu, kirangiza siporo, amateraniro y'idini, politiki n'umuco, kandi cyongera ubukene bw'ibikoresho kubera gutinya kugura.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa mu rwego rw'akarere mu bihugu 193, bibangamira hafi 99.4% by'abanyeshuri bose ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo kuri virusi yakwirakwijwe kuri interineti, kandi hari n'ibindi bikorwa byo gutinya igihugu no kucyanga bishingiye ku bwoko n'isura, byibasira Abashinwa, abandi baturutse mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Uburasirazuba bwa Aziya, n'abandi baturutse mu turere dufite virusi.
Kubera ko ingendo n'inganda zikomeye byafunze, umwuka wanduye n'umwuka wa karuboni byagabanutse.
Mu mujyi wa Wuhan (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) mu Bushinwa, abayobozi b'ubuzima batangaje ko hari abantu benshi banduye icyorezo cya Pneumonia ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, kandi ngo hatangijwe iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abenshi mu barwayi bakekwaho kwandura iyi virus bari mu isoko ryagurishwaga amafi yo mu bwoko bwa seafood muri Huanan, bityo bikaba byemezwa ko iyi virusi ishobora kuba yaraturutse mu nyamaswa.
Virusi yatumye habaho iki cyorezo, yitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni virusi nshya yavumbuwe ifitanye isano ya hafi na virusi ya Baturi, Coronavirus ya Bonrui na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere wagaragaje ibimenyetso, yaje kurwara ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; kandi nyuma yaho, ntaho bigaragara ko uwo muntu yari afitanye isano n'agatsiko k'isoko ry'amazi.
Mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019, iki kigo cyagaragaye ko gifite uruhare mu gutangiza icyiciro cya mbere cy'abanduye, aho abagera kuri bibiri bya gatatu by'abanduye bari mu cyiciro cya mbere.
Raporo itari yemewe yo ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020 yo mu kinyamakuru South China Morning Post yagaragaje ko ikibazo cya mbere cyabonetse ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019, gishobora kuba ari icy'umuntu w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko ubwandu bushya mu Bushinwa bwagabanutse, ariko bukaba bwarateye imbere mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, kandi ko umubare w'ubwandu bushya hanze y'Ubushinwa bwabanje kurenga umubare w'ubwandu bushya mu Bushinwa.
Umubare w'abandura ushobora kuba waragabanyijwe, cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Gashyantare, umubare muto w'abanduye wari urimo urubyiruko, abenshi bari munsi y'imyaka 19 kandi 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Umunyamabanga mukuru w'ubushakashatsi mu Bwongereza, Patrick Valence, avuga ko 60% by'abaturage b'u Bwongereza bagomba kwandura mbere y'uko bagira ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara.
Mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko, umubare w'abanduye ni umubare w'abantu basuzumwe COVID-19 bagasanga barwaye.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze gikora ibizamini birenze 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi ibihugu byinshi nka Italy, Ubuholandi, Esipanye na Suisse byashyizeho politiki yemewe yo kudakora ibizamini ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku ya 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko ku ya 23 Mutarama, hafi 86% by'abanduye COVID-19 mu Bushinwa bataraboneka, kandi ko 79% by'abanduye bataraboneka ari bo batumye habaho ubwandu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku ya 30 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani wari munini cyane ugereranyije n'uko byemezwa na leta.
Imibare y'ibanze y'umubare w'imbyaro (R0) ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 yari 1.4 kugeza kuri 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara bwavuze ko bishoboka ko ari 5.7.
Abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 barakira.
Ku bantu badafite ibimenyetso, igihe cyo gupfa kuva ibimenyetso byongereye kigera ku minsi 6 kugeza ku minsi 41, ariko ubusanzwe ni iminsi 14.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97,000 bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19.
Kugeza ku wa 5 Gashyantare, 80% by'abantu bapfuye mu Bushinwa bari bafite imyaka 60 n'abayirengeje, 75% muri bo bakaba barwaye indwara z'umutima na diyabete. Imibare y'ubutegetsi y'abapfuye ba COVID-19 akenshi yerekana abantu bari barwaye COVID nkuko bisanzwe bigenda.
Umubare w'abapfa bazira COVID-19 ushobora kuba munini cyane, kuko ushobora kuba utarimo abantu bapfa batageragejwe - nko mu ngo, mu bigo byita ku barwayi n'ahandi.
Hari amakuru y'ibice by'ingenzi yavuye mu Butaliyani agaragaza ko umubare w'abamaze gupfa mu gihe cy'icyorezo ari inshuro 4-5 z'abishwe na COVID.
"Umuvugizi w'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye ko ""tuzi ko [imibare y'abapfuye] ari ugushidikanya ku mibare y'ukuri"", ibi bikaba byemezwa n'amakuru adafite aho ahuriye n'ibarura rito ry'abanduye muri Amerika.
Umuntu wa mbere wapfuye hanze y'Ubushinwa ni uwa mbere mu gihugu cya Philippines ku ya 1 Gashyantare, naho uwa mbere mu gihugu cya France ku ya 14 Gashyantare.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 12 bamaze gupfa hanze y'ubutaka bw'u Bushinwa, muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo no mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, abantu bamaze gupfa mu bihugu n'uturere bisaga mirongo ine byo ku migabane yose y'isi uretse Antarctica.
Iyi mibare itandukanye bitewe n'akarere, kandi igengwa n'umubare w'ibipimo, ireme ry'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe cyashize kuva icyorezo cyatangira, n'ibintu by'abaturage birimo imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima muri rusange. Imibare y'urupfu n'ubwandu yerekana umubare w'abapfuye mu gihe runaka cy'igihe bagabanyijemo umubare w'abamaze kwandura.
Dukurikije imibare ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, imibare y'abapfuye n'abanduye ku isi yose ni 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare w'abapfuye utandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa n'abapfa wavuye kuri 17.3% (abafite ibimenyetso kuva ku ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020) ugera kuri 0.7% (abafite ibimenyetso bya mbere kuva ku ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ibindi bikoresho byo kwirinda ni igipimo cy'abapfa (CFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu bapfuye bazize indwara, n'igereranyo y'abapfuye bazize kwandura (IFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu bapfuye bazize indwara (bafite cyangwa badafite).
Ibipimo ntabwo ari iby'igihe gito kandi bikurikirana abantu batandukanye kuva banduye kugeza ku basanze banduye.
Intiti nyinshi zagiye zigerageza kubara imibare y'abantu bafite imibare yihariye.
Ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku buvuzi cy'i Kaminuza ya Oxford gitangaza ko umubare w'abapfa muri iki cyorezo uri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Ibitekerezo byatanzwe hejuru y'ubu buryo bihuza n'ibaruramari ryakozwe mu Budage ku isuzuma rya mbere rya COVID-19 mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo n'ingaruka z'ibipimo ku bipimo bya CFR.
OMS ivuga ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cyo kwibasira no kurangiza icyorezo ni kitamenyekana kandi gishobora gutandukana bitewe n'aho giherereye.
McKeownes Bonney wo muri kaminuza ya leta ya Penn, yaravuze ati "iyo indwara itarageragejwe, ubwandu bushobora kuba ari bwo butegeka, hanyuma bukagenda bugabanuka mu gihe nta wundi murwayi ufite".
Ariko muri iki gihe, biragoye cyane kuvuga igihe ibyo bizabera.
"Zhang Nanshan, umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi muri leta y'Ubushinwa, yavuze ko "bishobora kurangira muri Kamena" mu gihe ibihugu byose byahuza imbaraga kugira ngo bikurikize inama z'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) zo kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi".
"Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharsky wo mu ishuri ry'isuku n'ubuvuzi bw'ibihe byose ry'i Londres yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 "ishobora gukomeza gukwirakwira mu gihe cy'umwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri".
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Imperial College buyobowe na Neil Ferguson, bwagaragaje ko "gukomeza gukumira no gukurikiza andi mabwiriza ari ngombwa kugeza igihe habonetse urukingo (ushobora kuba amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko bidashoboka ko iyi coronavirus izashira burundu kubera ko yandura vuba cyane, kandi ko ishobora kuba ari indwara y'ibihe by'umwaka igaruka buri mwaka".
Uburemere bw'ibicurane bizaterwa n'ubwirinzi bw'amatungo n'uburemere bw'ubundi bwoko.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe, kandi abantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro (88%) n'igisebo cyumye (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara ni: gucogora, guhumeka, kubura akamero, guhumeka nabi, ububabare mu bice by'umubiri, ububabare mu muhogo, umutwe, kuribwa n'imbeho, kuruka, gutukana, guhumeka ikawa, guhumeka, cyangwa cyanose. WHO ivuga ko hafi umuntu umwe mu bantu batandatu arwara cyane kandi agahumeka nabi.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyashyize ku rutonde rw'ibimenyetso by'ingenzi umuntu agomba guhita ahita abona ubufasha bw'abaganga mu gihe ahumeka, agahinda cyangwa agahinda mu gatuza, guhungabana, guhaguruka no kugira ubururu cyangwa umunwa.
Hari bamwe bashobora kuba batagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubwandu, ariko ibizamini byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi bagasaba ko abantu bose bagiranye imishyikirano n'abanduye bagomba kugenzurwa no gupimwa kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
Imibare y'Abashinwa ivuga ko abarwayi badafite ibimenyetso ari bake, ariko ko ari 44%.
Icyiciro cy'ubuhumekero rusange (igihe cy'ubwandu n'ibimenyetso) kigera ku munsi umwe kugeza ku minsi 14; iminsi itanu. Mu ngero z'ibidasobanutse, ibice 30% by'abafite COVID-19 babanzaga kubona ubuhumekero bwa mbere, na 15% by'abaje kubona ubuhumekero nyuma.
Amakuru y'uburyo iyi ndwara yandura aracyategurwa.
Bitekerezwa ko iyi ndwara yandura ahanini mu gihe cyo guhuza ibitsina byimbitse no mu gihe cyo gukorora, kwitsamura cyangwa kuvuga; guhuza ibitsina byimbitse bivuze kuba hagati ya metero 1 na 2 (havuye kuri metero 3 kugeza kuri metero 6).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko umwotsi uturuka ku mwotsi ukorotse ushobora kugera kuri metero 4.5 (metero 15) kugeza kuri metero 8.2 (metero 27).
