OMS ivuga kandi ko hari imiti isanzwe n'indi ikoreshwa mu rugo ishobora gufasha mu kugabanya ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-19.
Kwiyongera kw'ubushobozi no kugura amavuriro y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 byasobanuwe na OMS nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda icyorezo.
ECDC na WHO Regional Office for Europe batanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bwa mbere agomba gukurwaho mu buryo bwinshi, harimo kongera ubushakashatsi mu mavuriro ku gupima COVID-19, kongera umubare w'abandura COVID-19 bakorerwaho isuzuma rikomeye, no gutoza abakozi, no kongera umubare w'abafite umwuka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku byerekeye aho ikibazo cya mbere (cyitwa "Patient Zero") gishobora kuba cyaraturutse.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye coronavirus y'ubwoko bushya yamenyekanye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu kwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus mu mujyi wa Hubei wariyongereye cyane.
Ibi byose byarebanaga n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, aho inyamaswa z'ibanze zagurishwaga, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yavuye mu nyamaswa imwe muri izo, cyangwa se ko ifite inkomoko mu nyamaswa. Ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, habonetse icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane by'uburwayi bw'ubwoko butaramenyekana, maze Dr. Zhang Jixian akajya kuvurira mu bitaro by'intara ya Hubei, maze abimenyesha CDC yo mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
"Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ku byerekeye ""virusi ya coronavirus isa na SARS".
Abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang, bakatiwe igipolisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha, naho undi muganga witwa Ai Fen, yahawe ruswa n'abakozi be bakuru kubera ko yavuze ko hari akaga.
Nyuma yaho, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umugi wa Wuhan yasohoye itangazo ku mugaragaro ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, maze imenyesha Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku Buzima (OMS).
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa mbere, Wuhan yagaragaje umubare munini w'abanduye icyorezo cya Pneumonia kitaramenyekana, cyakomeje kwiyongera, ku buryo mu ntangiriro z'iki cyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya 2020, virusi yageze mu bindi bice by'Ubushinwa, ibifashijwemo n'impunzi z'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa, kandi kubera ko Wuhan ari ihuriro ry'ingendo n'umuhanda munini w'indarayi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko abantu bashya 140 babonetse ku munsi umwe, barimo babiri bakomoka i Beijing n'umwe wo mu mujyi wa Shenzhen.
Amakuru y'ibanze yakurikiyeho yagaragaje ko abantu 6174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ni zo zabonye umubare munini w'abamaze kwandura mu isi, zirenga u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku itariki ya 9 Mata 2020, ku isi hose hamaze kuboneka abantu barenga 1.61 miliyoni; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye, abandi barenga 364,000 barakira.
Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 byiboneye nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije Uburayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza no gushyiraho amategeko ku mipaka.
Mu bisubizo by'igihugu harimo ingamba zo gukumira, nko gushyira abantu bose mu kato (urwego rwo kuguma mu rugo cyangwa urwego rwo gushakisha aho umuntu ashobora kuba ari) na guma mu rugo. Kugeza ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300 cyangwa 90% by'abaturage, bari mu bihe by'amabwiriza yo gufunga mu buryo runaka muri Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu bihe by'amabwiriza yo gufunga muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo n'abantu bagera kuri miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde bari mu bihe by'amabwiriza yo gufunga.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu bihe runaka byo gufunga imiryango, nyuma y'iminsi ibiri biyongeraho miliyari 2.6 - ni ukuvuga hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, Wuhan yabonye umuntu wa mbere wemejweho COVID-19, ariko amakuru adashyize mu gaciro avuga ko umuntu wa mbere wabonetse ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Muganga Zhang Jijian yabonye icyorezo cya Pneumonia ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, nyuma y'aho ibitaro bye byamenyesheje Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibipimo bya mbere by'imiterere y'ibimenyetso by'umurwayi byakozwe ku wa 27 Ukuboza 2019 byerekanye ko hari virusi ya corona isa na SARS.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umugi wa Wuhan yashyize ahagaragara itangazo.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (WHO) wabimenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
"Igihe ayo makuru yasohokaga, polisi yari irimo irakangurira abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan "gukwirakwiza ibihuha" by'icyorezo".
"Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya gifatika" cy'ubwandu bw'umuntu ku muntu".
"Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije gahunda y'impinduramatwara nyuma yaho Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, yavuze ko ari "intambara y'abaturage" yo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi".
"Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, i Wuhan hatangajwe gahunda yo kwirinda abantu benshi, bivugwa ko ari "igihembwe gikomeye kurusha ibindi byose mu mateka y'abantu", cyakwirakwijwe mu mijyi 15 muri Hubei, kigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miriyoni 57".
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byari bibujijwe mu mujyi.
Umunsi mukuru w'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki 25 Mutarama) wasubitswe mu bice bitandukanye.
Abayobozi batangaje ko hari hagiye kubakwa ibitaro by'agateganyo byitwa Huoshanshan Hospital, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma y'ibitaro bya Leishenshan, hari ikindi bitaro cyubatswe kugira ngo kijye kwita ku barwayi benshi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, ibindi bigo 14 by'i Wuhan, nk'ikigo cy'amakoraniro n'ikibuga, byongeye guhindurwa ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yafashe ingamba zo kwirinda icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutangaza iby'ubuzima ku ba mukerarugendo no kwagura iminsi mikuru ya Spring Festival.
Amashuri n'amashuri byarafunzwe mu gihugu hose.
Ibice bya Hong Kong na Macau byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku mashuri na kaminuza.
Imirimo yo gukorera kure yashyizweho mu bice bitandukanye by'Ubushinwa.
Ingendo zo kwinjira no gusohoka muri Hubei zarahagaritswe.
Ingendo za Leta zarahindutse mu Bushinwa hose, kandi amazu ndangamurage arafungwa by'agateganyo.
"Imiryango myinshi yashyizeho ingamba zo kugabanya urujya n'uruza rw'abantu, kandi abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bagerageje guhagarika ingendo zabo. Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo cyadutse ku isi hose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Abashinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kubuza virusi "kwinjira" mu bindi bihugu".
Urugero, Beijing yatangaje ko abashaka kujya mu mahanga bose binjira mu mujyi bagomba kwigenga mu gihe cy'iminsi 14. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, mu gihugu cy'u Bushinwa hagezweho umuntu umwe gusa wanduye, mu gihe hari hashize iminsi itanu.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, Li Keqiang, yavuze ko gukwirakwira kw'abanduye mu gihugu mu buryo bw'ibanze byahagaritswe, kandi ko icyorezo cyahagaritswe mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'amezi abiri ikigo cy'Ubushinwa cyashyizeho gahunda yo gufunga, ku munsi umwe, mu gihe cya Wuhan, ingamba zo kugabanya ingendo muri Hubei zarorohewe. Minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku wa 26 Werurwe 2020 ko uburenganzira bwo kwinjira ku bantu bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura buzahagarikwa guhera ku wa 28 Werurwe, kandi nta makuru arambuye yatangajwe igihe aya mabwiriza azarangirira.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula y'Ubushinwa.
Ubuyobozi bw'u Bushinwa bwateye inkunga ubucuruzi n'inganda kongera gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi butanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku bigo by'ubucuruzi. Inama ya Leta yatangaje umunsi w'icyunamo watangiye saa kumi za mu gitondo ku ya 4 Mata, umunsi wahariwe ibirori bya Qingming, nubwo leta y'u Bushinwa yasabye imiryango kujya yita ku bantu ku buryo bwa interineti mu gihe bakomezaga gutandukanya abantu kugira ngo birinde icyorezo gishya cya COVID-19.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo iturutse mu Bushinwa ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020.
Ikigo cy'ubuzima mu gihugu cyatangaje ko habonetse ubwandu bwinshi ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, ahanini bitewe n'umuteguro mushya w'idini ry'Abayahudi witwa Shincheonji Church.
Abashyitsi bavuye i Wuhan bajya i Daegu mu rusengero rwa Shinchangi, bakekwaho kuba ari bo batumye habaho icyo cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, 1,261 mu bayoboke 9,336 ba Kiliziya, cyangwa hafi 13%, bavuze ko bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite umuburo wo ku rwego rwo hejuru ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, muri Koreya hongeye kugaragara abantu barenga 2,000 banduye, ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare hazamukaho 3150.
Inzego zose za gisirikare zo muri Koreya y'Epfo zafatiwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bavuye mu gisirikare basanze banduye virusi ya Corona.
Amatariki y'indege nayo yagize ingaruka, bituma ahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yatangije gahunda yo gupima abantu virusi no gutandukanya abantu banduye no gushaka no gushyira mu kato abo bahuye nabo, iyi gahunda ikaba ifatwa nk'iyari nini kandi yateguwe neza ku isi.
Uburyo bwo gupima, harimo gutangaza ibimenyetso by'abantu bashya bahagera binyuze kuri porogaramu za terefone, gupima virusi binyuze mu modoka ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no gupima abantu 20,000 buri munsi.
Nubwo imijyi itakomeje gushyirwa mu kato, gahunda muri Koreya y'Epfo yabonetse nk'igikorwa cy'ibanze cyo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko basaba ko Moon yahanwa cyangwa bashima uko yabyitwayemo, bavuga ko icyorezo cyakoreshejwe nabi ku mugaragaro.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Korea y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite umubare muto w'abanduye umunsi umwe mu byumweru bine.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bashya bavuye mu mahanga bazajya bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ibyifuzo by'ibipimo bya virusi by'ibihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Irani yatangaje ku nshuro ya mbere icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu mujyi wa Qom ku ya 19 Gashyantare, aho abantu babiri bapfuye ku munsi wakurikiyeho nk'uko bitangazwa na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi.
Mu byo Leta yatangaje harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'indi mihango y'umuco n'imikino, gusiba amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu no gufunga amashuri, ibigo by'amashuri yisumbuye na za kaminuza.
Irani yatanze miliyari eshanu za riyal mu kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twibasiwe n'icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwinshi rwabaye hagati y'imijyi, mu gihe umwaka mushya wa Parsi wari wegereje.
Ibigo by'idini bya Shiite i Qom byari byuguruye kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Hagati y'ibyifuzo byo kugabanya ubukana bw'icyorezo muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byabonye Irani nk'isoko ry'ubwandu bwabo ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko ubukana bw'icyorezo bwari hejuru cyane y'ubwandu 388 bwatangajwe na leta ya Irani kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Irani yahagaritswe kubera ko 23 mu bagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko 290 basanze banduye virusi ya Corona.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Umugenzuzi w'uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura byanze bikunze abagizi ba nabi bafunzwe kubera imyivumbagatanyo y'amahoro, no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira.
Bivugwa ko ibigo by'imirimo by'uburoko, nk'amabohero, bifite ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi, kandi ko nta buvuzi buhagije bihabwa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, ari bo benshi cyane mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki n'abategetsi 12 ba Iran b'ubu cyangwa ba kera, bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, muri Irani habonekaga abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha, n'urupfu buri minota 10.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umukozi wa WHO, Iran ishobora kuba ifite abantu bakubye inshuro eshanu umubare w'abanduye.
Byongeye kandi, byasabwe ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kuba byangiza ubushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'ubukungu bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku burenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bikurwaho ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye ko cyandukiye mu Butaliyani ku wa 31 Mutarama, ubwo ba mukerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa mu mujyi wa Roma bagiraga SARS-CoV-2 y'ubwandu.
Abanduye batangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose zituruka mu Bushinwa, ndetse no gushyiraho ibihe by'ubukungu mu gihugu.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, mu mujyi wa Lombardy habonetse umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 nyuma y'ubwandu bwa 16 bwemejwe. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, inama y'abaminisitiri yashyizeho itegeko rishya rihana iki cyorezo, aho abantu barenga 50,000 bo mu mirenge 11 yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani bashyizwe mu kato.
Minisitiri w'Intebe, Giuseppe Conte, yavuze ko icyorezo cyatumye habaho inzitizi zo kwinjira no gusohoka mu bice byose.
"Mu turere tw'aho, ibikorwa byamaze guhungabana ndetse n'imikino yarahagaritswe. "Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza bifungwa burundu ku rwego rw'igihugu, kubera ko umubare w'abapfuye mu Butaliyani ugeze ku 100.
Nubwo imikino yose y'imikino ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya football, yagombaga kuba mu kwezi kwa kane, ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe byibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Inte yategetse ko ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi bifungwa, uretse amasupamaketi n'amafashini. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ishuri ry'Ubuvuzi, Ubuvuzi, Ubuzima no Kubungabunga (SIAARTI) ryatanze inama y'amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi ku byerekeye uburyo bwo kwivuza bushobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwatanze imibare y'abapfuye 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo, gisimbura Ubushinwa mu kuba igihugu cya mbere ku isi cyahitanye abantu benshi na coronavirus.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Uburusiya bwohereje mu Butaliyani indege icyenda z'ingabo zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Kugeza ku wa 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hamaze kugaragara abantu 128,948 banduye, 15,887 bapfuye, naho 21,815 bakize, cyane cyane mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN igaragaza ko guhuza umubare munini w'abantu bakuze bo mu Butaliyani n'ubushomeri bw'abanduye virusi bishobora gutuma habaho igipimo cyo hejuru cy'abapfa.
Mu mizo ya mbere, Ubwongereza ni bwo bwitabiriye neza cyane virusi kandi kugeza ku itariki ya 18 Werurwe 2020, ubuyobozi bw'Ubwongereza ntibwategetse abaturage bayo kwirinda mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose cyangwa gushyira abantu mu kato.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yanenzwe cyane kubera ko itumvaga ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku bantu. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko ingendo zose zidakenewe, imikoranire ya rubanda ihagaritswe, kandi ko yagiriye abantu inama yo gukorera mu rugo aho bishoboka, no kwirinda utubari, amazu y'uburiro n'amazu y'imyidagaduro.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'ibiruhuko nka za pub na za gym bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi yiyemeza gutanga umushahara w'abakozi 80% kugeza ku £2,500 ku kwezi mu rwego rwo gukumira ubushomeri muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zo kwirinda cyane abantu, kubuza guteranira hamwe abantu barenga babiri no guhagarika ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze gusa ku bintu bisabwa cyane.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'uburyo bwa mbere, izi ngamba zakurikizwaga na polisi, binyuze mu gutanga ibihano no gukuraho abantu mu makoraniro.
"Ubucuruzi bwinshi, harimo amasuporari, amaduka acuruza imiti, amabanki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ibikoresho, sitasiyo za lisansi n'amagaraji, byategetswe gufunga, uretse gusa ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi byafashwe nk'"ibikenewe".
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyamenyekanye bwa mbere mu ntara ya Pacific Northwest ya Washington, mu muntu umwe wari waturutse i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Igisirikare cya White House Coronavirus Task Force cyashinzwe ku wa 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange, kandi butegeka ko habaho ingendo z'abashyitsi baturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya US, Center for Disease Control, cyatangaje ko cyateguye ibikoresho by'igerageza.
Nyamara, Amerika yakoze ibizamini ku buryo buhoro cyane, bituma umubare w'abanduye mu gihe cy'icyorezo ugenda urenga ku mwotsi.
Ibizamini byahagaritswe n'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi by'ibyaha byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, hamwe no kutagira uburenganzira bwa leta ku bikoresho by'ubushakashatsi byigenga (amashuri, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare, ndetse n'ibikoresho by'ubugenzuzi abantu bafite kugirango bakwizeze ikizamini (kuva icyo gihe hagomba kuba itegeko rya muganga) kugeza mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe.
Kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, The Washington Post yatangaje ko muri Amerika hakorewe ibizamini bike cyane ku bantu 4,000.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hasigaye ibipimo 14.000.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara kandi bafite amabwiriza ya muganga, bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi myinshi kugira ngo bakore ibizamini". Ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, guverineri Joy Insley yatangaje ko leta ya Washington ari yo iri mu bihe by'ubukonje, intambwe yahise ikurikirwa n'izindi leta.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yafunze ibyiciro bya gatatu muri Werurwe, kandi amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yari arimo gufunga mu kwezi kwa gatatu. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo zo muri kaminuza ya Imperial College i Londres, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, zatanze inama ku ngaruka za coronavirus nshya mu gihugu no ku buryo bwo kuyitegura.
Ni umunsi Perezida Trump yemeyeho itegeko ryo kwishyura amafaranga y'inguzanyo ya Coronavirus Preparedness and Response Act, riha agera kuri miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari y'ubutabazi bw'ibigo bya leta mu rwego rwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe ategeka ko abakozi batembera, akabuza inama, kandi agatera abakozi inkunga yo gukorera mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibirori by'iminsi mikuru byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko atazemerera abantu kujya mu bihugu byinshi by'u Burayi, uretse u Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30 guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yongeye kwagura ibihano by'u Bwongereza na Ireland.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu cyose gifite ikibazo cy'ubukungu, bituma hashyirwaho amafaranga ya leta yo guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi muri Amerika bwafunze cyangwa bukora amasaha make mu rwego rwo kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe mu bihugu byose 50 no mu ntara ya Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, i New York City hagezweho 10,700 by'abanduye coronavirus, barenga umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, Guverineri yavuze ko politiki yo kwirinda abantu bagendana igaragara ko ikora, kuko imibare y'abanduye yagabanutse kuva kuri 2.0 kugeza kuri 4.7 ku munsi.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, New York City yari ifite abantu 32,308 banduye, naho 672 bahitanywe na virusi. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zari zifite umubare munini w'abanduye coronavirus kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zari zifite abantu 400,335 banduye, naho abantu 12,841 bakaba barapfuye.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda guhana intera kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort, bwari bufite ibitanda 1000, bwashyize inkingi mu mujyi wa New York.
Abantu 884 bishwe na Coronavirus muri Amerika mu masaha 24 yo ku ya 3 Mata.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, abantu barenga 100.000 bari baranduye muri Leta ya New York. White House yanenzwe kubera ko yirengagije ibi bimenyetso by'ubutagondwa, kandi igategeka ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence gushyiraho amabwiriza ku bayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu by'ikoranabuhanga kugira ngo bakore ibishoboka byose kugira ngo bahurize hamwe itangazo n'ibitabo by'itangazamakuru bijyanye na virusi.
Trump yemeye ko ikibazo cye cyakemurwa n'ishyaka rye.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze Amerika kubera ko ikomeza kugendera ku isoko ry'ibikoresho by'ingenzi by'ubuvuzi, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'u Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'uburyo indege zikora ryakoreshejwe mu gutegura no guhanura uburyo indwara zikwirakwira, kandi ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere 2020.
Abantu benshi bavuye i Wuhan baje i Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei, bishingiye ku makuru yo mu mwaka wa 2018 yavuye mu Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Inyambukiragutabara.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne nabyo byashyizwe ku rutonde rw'ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abashyitsi baturutse i Wuhan.
Muri 20 y'imigi y'ibanze ifite ibyokurya byinshi, Bali ni yo yabonye ubushobozi buke mu gihe muri Ositaraliya hari imigi yabonye ubushobozi buke. Australia yatangaje gahunda yayo yo gusubiza mu bihe by'ubukungu by'icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19) ku wa 7 Gashyantare.
Byari byemejwe ko hari byinshi bigomba kumenyekana kuri COVID-19 kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu gucunga imipaka no gutangiza itumanaho mu gusubiza iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, mu gihugu cya Ositaraliya hashyizweho ikibazo cy'umutekano w'ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ko imodoka za Leta zashyiriweho i Wuhan na Hubei mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gukura abaturage n'abakozi ba diplomasi mu karere, hakoreshejwe indege zahawe uburenganzira n'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa.
Ibihugu bya mbere byari byateguye gucyura abaturage babyo ni Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand.
Pakisitani yatangaje ko itazongera gucyura umuturage n'umwe mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuye abaturage 34 b'Abanyabrezili cyangwa imiryango yabo, usibye abapolisi bane, Umunyamerika umwe n'Umuhinde umwe.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde, bahagurukiye muri Polonye, aho indege ya Brazil yafashe urugendo mbere yo kujya muri Brezili.
Abaturage ba Brazil bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato mu kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Abakana 215 (176 mu ndege ya mbere na 39 mu ndege ya kabiri yahawe uruhushya na leta zunze ubumwe z'Amerika) bakuwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan muri uwo munsi bajyanwa muri CFB Trenton maze bahamara ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye abantu 185 bakomoka muri Canada yavuye i Wuhan igwa ku kibuga cy'indege cya CFB Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Australia bakuye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 z'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare, babajyana mu kigo cya Christmas Island, cyari cyarahinduwe ahantu ho kuguma mu kato, bakamarayo iminsi 14.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, indege y'abimukira yavuye muri Nouvelle-Zélande yageze i Auckland; abagenzi bayo (bari barimo bamwe baturutse muri Ositaraliya n'abo muri Pasifika) bari mu kato ku cyambu cya Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zizakura Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess Primo.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 yavuye kuri Diamond Princess ihagera i Trenton muri Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubuhinde yatangiye gucyura abaturage b'Abahinde muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yahawe na leta ya Afurika y'Epfo, yakuye abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Abaturage bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya Coronavirus, bagombaga kubanza kugenzurwa mbere yo kugenda, kugira ngo bakomeze kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura.
Abaturage ba Afurika y'Epfo bonyine bagaragaje ko batakiriho ni bo bahawe ubufasha bwo kugarura ubuzima.
Ibipimo byerekana ko abantu bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abashoferi, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare, bakekwaho kugira uruhare mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi, kandi ko abandi bose bazajya mu kato mu birori by'ubworozi mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho ingabo zayo muri Irani mu rugero bitewe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bateraniye muri Kaminuza yo muri Amerika kugira ngo bohereze imfashanyo mu duce tw'u Bushinwa twatewe na virusi. Bafatanyije n'itsinda ryo mu karere ka Chicago, boherereje ibitaro byo mu karere ka Hubei udupfukamunwa 50,000 tw'ubumara bwa N95.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya OMS yo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku nkingo n'ubuvuzi, ndetse no kurinda "abantu bafite ibyago muri Afurika no mu majyepfo ya Aziya".
Interactions yatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Philippines ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje mu mujyi wa Wuhan udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, umuryango wa Croix Rouge wa Singapore watangaje ko ugiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze agapfukamunwa ka miliyoni imwe muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko yatanze miliyoni 18 z'intoki z'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo udupfukamunwa 10,000, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, no gutanga inkunga y'amafaranga y'amadolari y'Amerika y'inyongera miliyoni 100 ku bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu butumwa bwo gufasha mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus mu Butaliyani.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho by'ipimisha bya miliyoni 1.1 muri Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda mu bihugu by'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho yohereje muri Panama ibikoresho 5,000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho bitanu byo guhumeka.
Mama na we yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada, agaragaza ko afite amakenga ku masike n'ibikoresho by'ibizamini byakozwe n'Abashinwa mu Buholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Czech.
Urugero, Esipanye yakuye ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima coronavirus byakozwe mu Bushinwa ku kigero cya 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwashubije udupfukamunwa 600,000 tw'Abashinwa twari dufite inenge.
Ububiligi bwasubije amasike 100,000 atagikoreshwa, byatekerezwaga ko byaturutse mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri byaturutse muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, mu bice bitandukanye bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika, abantu bakiriye neza ibyo Ubushinwa bwagezeho.
OMS yashimye cyane ingufu z'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa mu kugenzura no gucunga iki cyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'Abashinwa bashinjwaga kubungabunga ibanga, byabangamiye ibikorwa byo kucyirinda no kucyigenzura, n'ikibazo cyo muri iki gihe, aho leta y'u Bushinwa yatanze amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo yirinde ubwoba mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'icyunamo.
"Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu cyo gushyiraho gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo muri Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS, Goden Galley, yagize ati ""WHO rwose ntabwo yari yagihaye inama"", avuga ko ""ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cy'ubwitange bwo guhashya icyorezo ku isi aho cyibasiwe cyane"", avuga ko ari ""ntaho bihuriye mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange"". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemezwa kw'ikwirakwizwa hagati y'abantu mu Bushinwa no kwiyongera kw'imibare y'abandura mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cy'ubuzima rusange (Public Health Emergency of International Concern, PICHE), kikaba ari icya gatandatu kuva mu 2009 ubwo hatangazwaga icyorezo cya mbere cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane byo mu bwoko bwa Sinovirus".
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko PHEIC ari "impamvu y'uko ku isi hose, hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make cyangwa ari hagati, bidakeneye ubuvuzi bwiza".
Mu gusubiza ku iyubahirizwa ry'imihango yo kugabanya ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho ingamba zituma ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi bitagira icyo bitanga", yongeraho ko "WHO idashishikariza abantu kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gutegura ingamba mu bihugu bikennye, ivuga ko hari ibihugu bitagira uburyo bwo kumenya abo byahuye na virusi ndetse n'iyo yaba yarakingiwe.
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "dukomeye nk'uko umuntu w'intege nke cyane akomeye" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa nyuma". Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, WHO yatangije icyorezo cyitwa COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres, "yemeye gutanga imbaraga z'imiryango yose ya Loni mu gusubiza".
"Ibyo byatumye hashyirwaho itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo, ryemerera ibihugu byose guhuza ibisubizo, nk'uko WHO ibivuga, "bituma bigarura ibitekerezo ku bisubizo by'ubuzima, kandi ibindi bigo bigakoresha ubuhanga bwabyo mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'iki cyorezo ku rwego rw'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'imirimo ry'ubumwe riyobowe na WHO ryatangiye gukorana n'u Bushinwa mu kuzana itsinda ry'abahanga mpuzamahanga na WHO mu gihugu cya China kugira ngo bafashe mu gutunganya ubwandu mu gihugu, kandi basuzume ubukana n'ubushobozi bwo kubukwirakwiza binyuze mu nama n'ibigo by'igihugu by'ingenzi, kandi bagakora ingendo mu turere kugira ngo barebe ingaruka n'ibisubizo by'ibikorwa ku rwego rw'intara n'intara, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, WHO yatangaje ko isi yagombaga kurushaho kwitegura iki cyorezo cya coronavirus, ivuga ko nubwo kitari icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba gukomeza gutegura.
"Mu gusubiza icyorezo cya Iran, WHO yoherejeyo itsinda ry'abakozi ba WHO kugira ngo barebe uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, WHO yatangaje ku mugaragaro ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ku isi kizazamurwa kuva ku "cyinshi" kigashyirwa ku "cyinshi cyane", kikaba ari cyo cyiciro cyo hejuru cyo kuburira no kugenzura ibyago".
" Mike Ryan, umuyobozi ushinzwe ibikorwa by'ubutabazi mu rwego rw'ubuzima muri OMS, mu itangazo yatanze yatanze umuburo agira ati ""Ni ikigeragezo cy'ukuri kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: byuka".
"Iki cyorezo gishobora kuba kiri hafi kandi ugomba kuba witeguye", kugira ngo ufashe isi kwirinda "icyorezo gikomeye kurusha ibindi".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu adaha ibimenyetso by'uko abayobozi b'ubuzima rusange bashobora gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza ko ari icyorezo bizaba bisobanura ko "twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azagerwaho na virusi".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe iby'ubuvuzi yavuze ko WHO "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo ndetse n'icyorezo cy'icyorezo, ndetse n'icyorezo cy'icyorezo. WHO yahawe ibisobanuro byinshi kubera ko nta buryo buhagije bwo kugenzura icyorezo, harimo gutangaza ko habonetse ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange kandi ko kitari cyemewe na leta".
Mu bitekerezo by'ibinyoma harimo inyandiko isaba ko Tedros Adhanom, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO, yegura, yasinywe n'abantu 733.000 kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu za ONU zigera kuri mirongo imwe n'imwe zasobanuye ko uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bufite agaciro mu gihe cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko abantu bose bafite uburenganzira bwo gukora ibikorwa by'ubutabazi kandi ko Leta ari yo igomba kubikora.
Ishyaka ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima bitazigera biba impamvu yo kurobanura ku butoni.
Impuguke zashimangiye ko abantu bafite ubumuga, abagize amoko mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abatagira aho baba, abatishoboye, abafite ubukene bukabije, abafunzwe, impunzi n'abandi bantu batishoboye bakeneye ubufasha bwa leta, bose bafite uburenganzira ku buzima.
Ibigo bya leta mpuzamahanga birimo kwita ku ngaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza byatewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango wita ku Bwiyunge n'Iterambere (OECD) watangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru ajyanye n'igihe, amakuru arambuye ku bisubizo by'amabwiriza mu bihugu byo ku isi, ndetse no gutanga ibitekerezo n'inama.
Gahunda y'ubukungu ku isi ikubiyemo uburyo bwo gukurikirana politiki y'igihugu, kuva ku buryo bwo gukomeza imibereho myiza y'abaturage, ingendo, guhangana n'ingaruka z'ibigo bya digitale no gukinga ingaruka za Guma mu Rugo, kandi bigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku bindi no koroshya guhuza isi mu guhangana n'imbogamizi za Coronavirus.
Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Minisitiri w'Ubwongereza ushinzwe ibiro bya Minisitiri w'Intebe, Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil, Zayer Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro banenze leta y'u Bushinwa ku buryo ikurikirana icyorezo cyatangiriye mu karere ka Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abategetsi b'intara benshi b'ishyaka rya gikomunisti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe kubera imihati yo gushyira abantu mu kato mu karere ka China rwagati, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko hari urwikekwe mu nzego za politiki ku cyorezo cyibasiye utwo turere.
Bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko iki cyemezo cyafashwe mu rwego rwo kurinda Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, kugira ngo adakomeza kurakazwa n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Abashinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, bahakanye ibitekerezo by'ubufatanyacyaha ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 byaturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani, bahakana ibyo bavugaga mbere ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan.
"Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika buvuga ko coronavirus ari ""virusi y'Abashinwa"" cyangwa ""virusi ya Wuhan"" buvuga ko ""kugenzura kwa China byongereye virusi ubu imaze kuba icyorezo ku isi"", ibyo bamwe mu banenga babyita ivangura no "gushakisha kuyobya abantu ku byerekeye ukuntu ubutegetsi bwe bwananiwe gukumira iyi ndwara".
"Ikinyamakuru Daily Beast cyatangaje ko leta ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika yasobanuye uburyo bwo gushyikirana n'ibimenyetso byo mu Nama y'Umutekano w'Igihugu, aho iyo nzira yavuzwe ko ari "ibyo mu Bushinwa byose".
"Twabwiwe kugerageza gukwirakwiza ubutumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo ikiganiro n'abanyamakuru no kuba kuri televiziyo. " Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Politiki y'Amahanga na Bloomberg byatangaje ko ingufu z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukwirakwiza imbaraga ku isi.
"Umuyobozi w'umushinga w'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi, Joseph Borel, yaburiye ko hari "igice cya politiki gihereranye n'akarere, gikubiyemo "gukora inkuru no guharanira kugira ingaruka binyuriye ku "" politiki y'ubwigenge """.
"Borrell yongeyeho ati ""Ubushinwa burimo butanga ubutumwa bw'uko, mu buryo butandukanye na Amerika, ari cyo gihugu gifite inshingano kandi cyiringirwa". ""
Ubushinwa bwasabye Amerika kenshi guhagarika inkunga yabwo muri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, nyuma y'uko byatangajwe ko ari bwo bwiteguye kohereza imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu bibiri.
Imfashanyo ya Jack Ma y'ibirashe by'umubiri 100,000 byatanzwe muri Cuba byahagaritswe n'ibihano bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bashinjwa gukoresha inkunga bahaga ibindi bihugu mu gufasha igihugu cyabo.
Ibiganiro ku bijyanye n'imyenda y'abantu byabereye mu Budage, muri Otirishiya no mu Busuwisi, no mu bindi bihugu nka Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Turukiya kandi yafashe ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi by'ubwubatsi by'abakozi ba leta ya Turukiya.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi kubera kubura ubufatanye mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, Maurizio Massari, yavuze ko Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwitabiriye ku buryo bwa bilateral.
"Nta gushidikanya ko atari ikimenyetso cyiza ku bufatanye bw'ibihugu by'i Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ikiganiro cya telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani, Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'Uburusiya, Vladimir Putin, yategetse ingabo z'Uburusiya kohereza mu Butaliyani abaganga ba gisirikare, imodoka zihariye z'ubumara bw'ubumara n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
"Mu kinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa, "umuntu utazwi witwa ""umutegetsi ukomeye mu bya politiki"" yavuze ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo z'Uburusiya zari ""izitari ngombwa cyangwa zitari ngombwa ku Butaliyani""".
"Uru rubuga rwashinje u Burusiya kujya mu gikorwa cyo gushimisha "mu buryo bwa "geopolitique na dipolomasi".
Perezida wa Lombardy Attilio Fontana na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani Luigi de Mayo banze ibyo bitangazamakuru, maze babishimira.
Uburusiya bwongeye kohereza indege itwara ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
"Dimitry Peskov, umuvugizi wa Kremlin, yavuze ko "iyo bigeze ku gufasha bagenzi be b'Abanyamerika, [Putin] atekereza ko igihe abahanga mu by'imiti bo muri Amerika bazaba bafite imbaraga, na bo bazatanga umusanzu wabo".
"Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO ""Defender 2020"" iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye n'ibihugu by'Abanya-Baltique, ni imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO ikomeye cyane kuva intambara y'Ubutita irangiye, izakorwa ku rugero ruciriritse".
