Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bizwi nka "hygiène des mains", byerekeza ku gikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki z'umuntu agamije gukuraho ubutaka, ibishyimbo, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
"Gukaraba intoki buri gihe n'isabune mu "bihe by'ingenzi" by'umunsi, bigabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'ibicurane na kolera, byandurira mu byondo no mu kanwa".
Abantu bashobora kandi kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa imbeho, urugero, iyo badakarabye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa (ni ukuvuga mu maso).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi by'umunsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa ni: mbere na nyuma yo gukaraba, nyuma yo gukaraba cyangwa guhindura impapuro z'ibanga, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere na nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro cyangwa gukorakora inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, WHO, rigira riti "kugeza igihe cyo gukaraba intoki, ni byiza cyane.
Mbere yo guteka, mu gihe cyo guteka na nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura impapuro z'ibanga cyangwa gusukura ubwiherero bw'umwana.
Nyuma yo gukorora, gukorora cyangwa gukorora.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku biribwa by'amatungo cyangwa ku myanda yayo.
Isuku y'amaboko mu buvuzi yerekeza ku myidagaduro y'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kwitabwaho mu buryo bwa muganga bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki ni ukuzirinda mikorobe (bakteriya, virusi, cyangwa izindi mikorobe zishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho byangiza cyangwa bishobora gutera indwara.
Ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bita ku mirire cyangwa bakora mu by'ubuvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ubwandu bwa virusi zandura, virusi ya corona n'izindi ndwara; kwirinda indwara zandura ziterwa n'ibicurane; kugabanya ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero;
no kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa mu gihe cyo kubyarira mu rugo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki ishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu batagira uburebure.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, impinduka z'imyitwarire zisanzwe nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune zishobora kugabanya impfu z'abana ziterwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero n'ibicurane.
Ubu buryo bworoshye bushobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bazize iyi ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya igifu ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, kandi bishobora kugereranywa no kubona amazi meza mu duce dufite ubukene buke.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune bifitanye isano no kugabanya ibyago byo gucibwamwo ku kigero cya 48%. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bw'ibanze kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda gucibwamwo n'ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero (ARI) bukomeye, kandi bikorwa nk'umugenzo usanzwe mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage hirya no hino ku isi.
Pneumonia, ari na yo ARI ikomeye, ni yo mpamvu y'ibanze ituma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu bapfa. Ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Ubwonko n'imyimba ni byo bihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 3.5 buri mwaka.
Nk'uko UNICEF ibivuga, guhindura imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo gukaraba bishobora gukiza ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha inkingo cyangwa ubuvuzi, bigatuma abantu bapfa bazira gucibwamwo bagapfa kimwe cya kabiri, kandi bagapfa kimwe cya kane bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye.
Gukaraba intoki bihuzwa n'indi gahunda y'isuku nk'igice cy'amahugurwa y'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki birinda indwara z'uruhu zandura (impetigo) zandura binyuze mu guhura n'umuntu.
Ingaruka z'ibanze z'imyenda yo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutuma uruhu rugira ibyangombwa by'uko rwumye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gihugu cya Danimarike mu mwaka wa 2012, bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cyo kuribwa, kuruka, cyangwa se indwara y'uruhu rw'amaboko, cyane cyane mu bakozi b'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara yo guhangayika cyane (OCD).
Mu gihe cyo gukaraba intoki n'isabune, ni ngombwa ko umuntu akoresha amazi n'isabune mu gihe cyo gukaraba intoki, kugira ngo akureho indwara ziterwa n'imyanya y'ubuhumekero.
Indi mikoro yo gukaraba intoki ikwiye kugira ngo umuntu yirinde kwandura indwara, ni mbere na nyuma yo gukata cyangwa gukubita; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora, cyangwa gukaraba; nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa kuyitwara; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, abantu ntibakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2015 ku bihugu 54 ku bijyanye no gukaraba intoki, bwagaragaje ko ku kigero cya 38.7% by'imiryango ikoresha isabune. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2014 bwagaragaje ko muri Arabiya Sawudite ari ho higanje ku kigero cya 97%, muri Amerika ho hakaba hari hagati ya 77%, mu Bushinwa ho hakaba hari hasi cyane ni 23%.
