Amazi ashyushye yo gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ngo yice mikorobe.
Iyo mikorobe ikura vuba cyane iyo ifite ubushyuhe bw'umubiri (37°C).
Ariko kandi, amazi ashyushye n'isabune ni ingirakamaro cyane kurusha amazi akonje n'isabune mu gukuraho amavuta kamere afata ubutaka n'udukoko.
Ariko kandi, mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko abantu benshi babyemera, ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta ngaruka bigira ku kugabanya ibiro by'udukoko turi mu ntoki.
Igisukisha intoki kitariho amazi cyangwa umuti wica imibu utariho amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho by'isuku y'amaboko bitagira amazi (byitwa kandi amashashi ashingiye kuri alcohol, amashashi y'amaboko ya antiseptic, cyangwa isuku y'amaboko) byatangiye gukundwa.
Kugira ngo byorohere gukoresha no kugabanya ingaruka zo gukama kwa alkol, isopropyl alcohol cyangwa ethanol ahanini byakozwe hamwe na carbomer (polymeri ya acrylic acid) cyangwa humicant nka liquide cyangwa glycerine mu busa.
Kongera imyunyu ya idrogeni-peroxide byongera ibikorwa bya antimicrobial. Sanitizer y'amaboko ifite alcohol iri hagati ya 60 na 95%, ikaba ifite ubushobozi bwo kwica udukoko.
Inzoga z'ibinyabutabire bica mikorobe, mikorobe z'ubwoko bwinshi zidakira imiti (MRSA na VRE), igituntu na virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccinia, influenza na hepatite) n'iminkanyari.
Inzoga z'ibinyabiziga zirimo 70% ya alkali yica 99.97% (3.5 log reduction, ni kimwe no kugabanya 35 decibel) nyuma yo gukoreshwa ku ntoki amasegonda 30, no kwica 99.99% kugeza 99.999% (4 kugeza kugabanya 5 logs) ya bagiteri nyuma yo gukoreshwa ku ntoki umunota umwe. Inzoga z'intoki ni zo zikora cyane ku bagiteri, kandi ntizikora cyane ku mikorobe imwe.
Inzoga zikorerwa mu gukaraba intoki ni zo zikunze gutera indwara z'uruhu, kandi ntizikora neza ku ndwara ya Norovirus (cyangwa Norvac).
Amazi, udupfundikizo cyangwa ingeri, bikomeza gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 ku ntoki zombi, imbere n'inyuma, hagati y'intoki n'impande zazo kugeza bikamye.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyasabye ko umuntu yakwihana neza akoresheje umuti ukanahumanya intoki, cyane cyane iyo ari intoki zanduye.
Gukoresha ibyo bikoresho byongereye ku buryo byoroshye kubikoresha no ku buryo byangiza mikorobe vuba; nubwo nta mazi n'isabune biboneka, ntibikwiye gukoreshwa nk'uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki.
Iyo amabwiriza atagaragaje ko hari imboga cyangwa imboga z'ibanze zikoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki, bishobora gutuma umuntu agira uruhu rwumye.
Gushyira glycerine na/cyangwa indi mihindagurikire mu buryo bishobora kugabanya cyangwa gukumira ingaruka zo kumena inzoga.
Mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bifite inzoga byongereye cyane ubushyuhe n'umunaniro kurusha isabune cyangwa umuti wica udukoko.
Indwara z'uruhu ziterwa n'indwara ziterwa n'ubushye, indwara ziterwa n'ubushye cyangwa se uburwayi bwo kumva inzoga cyangwa ibintu byanduye mu nzoga, ni ibintu bidakunze kubaho mu gihe umuntu afashe ku ngufu inzoga.
Ku rundi ruhande, kudahanagura ibiganza n'isabune n'amazi, byatumaga umuntu agira ibyago byo gutangira indwara z'uruhu zituruka ku guhanahana ibintu.
Nubwo ari ingirakamaro, ibikoresho bitagira amazi ntibikuraho imyanda iri mu biganza, ahubwo bihumanya gusa intoki.
Kubera ko mikorobe zikomeza kuba ku ntoki, hari izindi mikorobe zidakora neza nk'amazi n'isabune.
Imikorere ya sanitizer itarimo inzoga ishingiye cyane ku bikoresho no ku gutunganya, kandi mu bihe byashize yakoze ku buryo buhambaye cyane kurusha inzoga n'ibinyobwa bisukura intoki.
Vuba aha, ibikomoka kuri benzalkoniyumu chloride byerekanye ko bikomeza kugira imikorere ya antimicrobial idakumira kandi idakumira, bitandukanye n'inzoga, ishobora kuba yagabanyutse mu mikorere nyuma yo kuyikoresha kenshi bitewe n'imiterere mibi y'uruhu igenda ikura.
Mu baturage bafite amikoro make, abantu benshi ntibagira amafaranga yo kugura isabune, ahubwo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ubutaka.
Umukungugu cyangwa ibumba bishobora kuba ari ingirakamaro kurusha amazi gusa, ariko bishobora kuba ari ingirakamaro cyane kurusha isabune.
Ikintu cy'ingenzi cyateye impungenge ni uko iyo ubutaka cyangwa umukungugu byandujwe na mikorobe, bishobora gutuma indwara zikwirakwira aho kugabanya.
Nk'uko bimeze ku isabune, umwotsi ni umuti wica udukoko kuko iyo uhuye n'amazi, utuma habaho umuti urimo alkali.
Mu gihe nta sabuni iboneka, OMS isaba ko umuntu yakoresha umukungugu cyangwa umusenyi mu gihe ashatse kuyisiga.
Uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki, buvugwa n'Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, bugomba kuba burimo:
Jya wima intoki mu mazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Amazi ni yo ahanini akoreshwa kuko amazi y'ibanze ashobora kwanduzwa, ariko ubushyuhe bw'amazi ntibuba buhindura ibintu.
Fata isabune uyikoreshe ku biganza, mu ntoki no munsi y'intoki, hanyuma usukure.
Isabuni ikuraho mikorobe mu ruhu kandi ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko abantu bakaraba intoki neza iyo bakoresheje isabune aho gukoresha amazi gusa.
Fata nibura amasegonda 20.
Iyo umuntu asukuye, agira umwanda, bityo bikuraho mikorobe, kandi iyo amaze igihe kirekire asukuye, bikuraho n'izindi mikorobe.
Jya ukaraba neza mu mazi.
Guhanagura intoki mu kidendezi bishobora kongera kwanduza intoki.
Jya ukaraba neza cyangwa se ubireke bikongoke.
Ibiganza byumye kandi byumye birushaho kwanduzwa. Ahantu habi cyane habuze ni ku ntoki, ku nkokora, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'amano.
Amagi y'ibumba n'ibishushanyo by'iminwa bishobora kurinda mikorobe.
