Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2008 na Paper Towel Industry European Tissue Symposium, kandi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster mu mujyi wa London, bwagereranyije ibipimo by'isuku itangwa n'utuwugi tw'impapuro, imashini zimesa amazi ashyushye n'imashini zimesa amazi ahumura.
