Ikigo gitera imvura cyitwa Jet-Air Dryer, cyakoreshaga umwuka mu gihe cy'isaha ya 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), cyashoboraga guhumeka mikorobe mu ntoki no mu bikoresho, kandi kikarinda ababikoreshaga ndetse n'ibidukikije by'aho bakoreshaga kugeza kuri metero 2.
Gukoresha igikoresho cyo kumesa intoki mu kirere cy'ubushyuhe, byatuma udukoko duto duto tw'ibinyabuzima dutembera ku metero 0.25 uvuye ku gikoresho cyo kumesa intoki.
Imyenda y'impapuro ntiyerekanye ikwirakwira ry'ibinyabuzima. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt mu 2005 bwagaragaje uburyo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, habonetse impinduka zikurikira mu miterere ya za mikorobe:
Hariho ubwoko bwinshi bw'ibikoresho byo kumesa intoki, kandi hari abagereranya ibyo kumesa intoki n'ibyo kumesa impapuro.
Mu gihe umuntu ari mu ngendo, gukoresha ibikoresho by'isuku mu gihe nta sabuni cyangwa amazi bihari, ni uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki.
Inzoga z'amaboko zirimo nibura 60% by'inzoga.
Gukaraba intoki mu by'ubuvuzi byabaye ngombwa nyuma y'igihe kirekire Ignaz Semmelweis, umuganga w'Umuhungari, avumbuye akamaro ko gukaraba intoki mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro (mu 1846).
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bifasha abakozi bo mu bitaro kwibuka niba baribagiwe gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukoresha izo nkingo byagabanyije umubare w'abandura.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'amasegonda 15 byibura, ukoresheje isabune n'amazi ahagije cyangwa se gel kugirango ukureho imyanda ku ntoki.
Inzoka zigomba gukomatana, intoki zikagomba gukorakora.
Iyo hasi y'amano hari umwanda, ushobora gukoreshwa n'isuku yo mu bwoko bwa brush.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuba mu mazi y'intoki, ni ngombwa ko ukaraba neza umubavu, ukayuhanaguza n'utweso twera.
Nyuma yo gukama, ukoresha umwenda w'impapuro mu gufunga amazi (kandi ukingura irembo ry'inyuma kugira ngo usohoke niba ari ngombwa).
Ibyo bituma ibiganza bitongera kwanduzwa n'ibyo bintu.
"Intego yo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi ni ukwirinda indwara ziterwa n'udukoko (""udukoko "") kandi tukirinda ko twanduzwa".
Ikinyamakuru New England Journal of Medicine cyatangaje ko mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, abantu benshi batigeze bakaraba intoki, aho abaganga n'abaforomo benshi bibagirwaga gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bigatuma habaho ubwandu bw'udukoko.
Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko gukaraba intoki neza n'ubundi buryo bworoshye bishobora kugabanya ku kigero cya 66 ku ijana ubwandu bw'amaraso bufitanye isano na catheter.
Amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi bw'amaboko yashyizweho na OMS ku rubuga rwayo, ashobora kuboneka ku rubuga rwayo kugira ngo abantu bayagezeho.
Isuzuma ry'ibyabaye ryakorewe na Whitby n'abandi.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kugenzura isuku y'amaboko mu gihe bibaye ngombwa ko hakorwa igenzura ry'ubuyobozi.
