"Nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi. Gushyira imiti mu isabune ("ibikoresho" cyangwa "insukoni" z'uburozi) bituma ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki byangiza".
Mu gihe cyo kubaga cyangwa mu gihe hari ahantu higanje abantu batagira umuti wa antibiotique, umuntu ashobora guhura n'ikibazo cyo guhunga. Kugira ngo umuntu akore iyo porogaramu, ni ngombwa ko agira umugozi wo gukaraba intoki, ukamwambura cyangwa ukamufunga udakozeho, agakoresha chlorhexidine cyangwa iodine, agakoresha isuku mu gihe cyo gukaraba intoki, kandi agakoresha ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuhumekero.
Inkweto zose zigomba gukingurwa.
Ubusanzwe, iyo myitozo iba igusaba ko ukaraba intoki n'amavi mu gihe cy'iminota ibiri cyangwa itandatu.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe kirekire (iminota 10) si ngombwa.
Mu gihe cyo gukaraba, amazi ava mu nkokora agera ku nkokora agomba kurindwa ngo atagaruka ku nkokora.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, intoki ziruma n'igitambaro kitagira ubwandu, kandi bakambara ikanzu y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo udukoko twanduze tugabanuke, ni byiza ko umuntu akaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye cyangwa agakoresha umuti wica udukoko.
Mu kugenzura kwandura kwa staphylococcus mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu nyinshi zo gukaraba intoki zaturutse ku 20% by'ibikoresho by'ibanze byo gukaraba intoki, kandi ko inyungu nke z'inyongera zatanzwe igihe bakomezaga gukaraba intoki hejuru ya 35%.
Guhana intoki n'isabune ya antibacterial mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'umuti usanzwe wa alcohol, buri kimwe cyagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'inzoga byagabanyije ubwandu bwa bacteria ku kigero cya 26% kurusha isabune ya antibacterial.
Ariko, isabune n'amazi birusha ingufu gukaraba intoki bishingiye kuri alcohol mu kugabanya virusi ya H1N1 influenza A n'inkondo ya Clostridium difficile mu ntoki. Mu rwego rwo kunoza isuku y'intoki mu bigo nderabuzima, bishobora kuba bikubiyemo kwigisha abakozi ku bijyanye no gukaraba intoki, no kwibutsa abakozi mu nyandiko no mu magambo ku bijyanye no kuboneka kw'intoki zishingiye kuri alcohol.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwimbitse ku bijyanye n'uburyo bwo kuvura bufite akamaro mu buzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kubona ubuzima bwiza, ndetse n'imirire myiza.
Ariko, kubura amazi yizewe, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo z'abantu, ku ishuri no ku kazi, bituma abantu badashobora kugira akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro muri Afurika, hari uburyo buhendutse bwo gukora aho bakaraba intoki, ariko nta na rimwe hari aho bakaraba hafi y'ubwiherero bwa bwite cyangwa bwa rusange.
Ariko kandi, kuba abantu bakoresha amazi make mu gihe cyo gukaraba bishobora kuba biterwa n'imyitwarire yabo yo kwiyuhagira mu buryo bwimbitse, aho kuba biterwa no kubura isabune cyangwa amazi.
Guteza imbere no gutanga inama ku bijyanye no gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro y'amabwiriza, byongera ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki, kandi bigatuma abantu bahindura imyitwarire yabo mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ikore neza, ikeneye kugenzurwa no gusuzumwa.
"Igikorwa cyo gusubiramo ibyigisho 70 cyagaragaje ko uburyo bw'abaturage mu bigo by'amashuri by'abikorera (LMIC) bukora neza mu gukaraba intoki, mu gihe ibikorwa byo kwamamaza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga bitagikora neza. Urugero rw'uburyo bwo gukangurira amashuri gukaraba intoki ni gahunda ya "Ukuntu 3 kw'inyenyeri" ya UNICEF, ishishikariza amashuri gushyiraho ingamba zoroshye, z'ingengo y'imari kugira ngo abanyeshuri bakomeze gukaraba intoki n'isabune, mu bindi bintu by'isuku bikenewe".
Iyo ibipimo by'ibanze byamaze kugerwaho, amashuri ashobora kugera ku nyenyeri eshatu kuva ku imwe kugeza ku yindi.
Gushyiraho sitasiyo yo gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bigize gahunda yo gukaraba intoki igamije kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi Mpuzamahanga w'Ubukangurambaga ni indi ngero y'ibikorwa byo gukangurira abantu guhanagura imyitwarire.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe na bumwe bwagaragaje ko kudahana mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere ari byo byatuma umuntu ahangana n'ikibazo cyo gukaraba intoki.
Ariko kandi, hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune bihenze cyane ugereranyije n'andi mavuriro n'isuku.
"Ingingo yo gukaraba intoki ku buzima bwa muntu - cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibibazo, urugero nk'ababyeyi bavuka mu bitaro cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse - byemejwe n'abapayiniya babiri b'isuku y'intoki mu kinyejana cya mbere: Ignaz Semmelweis, umuganga w'Umuhungari wakoraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya, na Florence Nightingale, "Umushinga w'ubuforomo bwa none" mu cyongereza".
Kugeza icyo gihe, abantu benshi bemeraga ko indwara yatewe n'umwotsi mubi witwa miasmus.
Mu myaka ya za 80, icyorezo cy'indwara ziterwa n'ibiribwa n'ubwandu bufitanye isano n'ubuzima byatumye ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara no kwirinda kirushaho gukangurira abantu gukoresha ibiyobyabwenge mu gihe cyo gukaraba intoki, nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyabaye mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyabaye mu 2020, byatumye ibihugu byinshi byongera ubumenyi ku bijyanye n'akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda iyi ndwara.
"Nk'urugero, mu Budage, ibishushanyo byerekana ""uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki neza"" byashyizwe ku byumba bya rubanda no iruhande rw'ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu mazu y'ibiro by'ibiro n'ahantu ho gukaraba ku bibuga by'indege".
"Iyi mvugo ngo "guhagurutsa umuntu" isobanura ko umuntu adashaka kwemera ko hari icyo yakoze cyangwa ko hari icyo yakoze".
Ikomoka mu gice cya Bibiliya cya Matayo aho Pontius Pilate yahagaritse umwanzuro wo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko ubu ikoreshwa cyane mu ndimi zimwe na zimwe z'icyongereza.
Muri Shakespeare, Macbeth, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki mu rwego rwo gusukura ikizira cy'ubupfapfa cye, agaragaza ko ari we wahemukiye umugabo we kubera icyaha yakoze.
Nanone kandi, byagaragaye ko abantu, iyo batekereje ku bikorwa by'ubwiyandarike, bakunda gukaraba intoki kurusha abandi, kandi ko bakunda guha agaciro cyane ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
"Byongeye kandi, abantu bakaraba intoki nyuma yo gukora bene ibyo bikorwa, ntibashobora gukora indi mirimo yo kwishyura "gukaraba" nk'uko bikorwa n'abakorerabushake".
Amadini yigisha gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku no mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, ni ugukoresha amazi/amazi mu gukaraba intoki ariko ntiwifashishe isabune, ni kimwe mu bikorwa by'idini biranga amadini menshi, harimo idini rya Bahá'í, idini ry'Abahindu, idini rya Tevilah n'iry'Abatari mu idini ry'Abayahudi, idini rya Lavo'bo mu idini rya Gikristo n'idini rya Ozu mu idini rya Isilamu.
Gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero ni itegeko mu idini ry'Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abayisilamu.
Kandi, gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma ya buri gihe mu bahindu, ababuda, abasiki, abayahudi n'abayisilamu ni itegeko.
Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19
Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19 ni ugushyira mu bikorwa ingamba zo kwirinda no kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gucunga ibyago mu kazi neza bishingiye ku kazi no ku kazi, ku igenzura ry'ibyago bituruka ku isoko ry'ubwandu, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo bashobora kuba bafite COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'Ikigo cy'Umutekano n'Ubuzima mu Mirimo (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago bike byo guhura n'abantu benshi hamwe n'abandi bakozi ni akazi gafite umubare muto w'abantu bakorana, aho ingamba zo kwirinda kwandura zisanzwe zisabwa harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kubahiriza amabwiriza yo guhumeka, no gusukura no gusubiza ibidukikije mu buryo bw'ibanze.
Imirimo yo mu rwego rwo hagati irimo gukorana n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko ikeneye gukorana kenshi cyangwa mu buryo bwa bugufi n'abantu bashobora kuba barwaye kubera indwara zikwirakwira mu baturage cyangwa se kubera ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri bo harimo abakozi bafite aho bahurira n'abaturage, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo imirimo myinshi, n'ahandi hahurira abantu benshi.
Uretse ingamba zo mu rwego rwo kwirinda icyorezo cya mbere, ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago kuri uyu muryango zirimo guhumeka hakoreshejwe imashini zigezweho zo guhumeka, kurinda ubwonko no gushyiraho ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite mu gihe umuntu ahanganye na COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi b'ubuzima n'abakora mu mirimo y'ubuvuzi bafite ibyago byo guhura n'abantu bafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho. Ibyago birushaho kwiyongera iyo abo bakozi bakoresheje uburyo bwo gukora aerosol cyangwa bakagura cyangwa bagakora ibipimo by'abantu bafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho.
Ingamba z'ibyago zikwiye ku bakozi ni iz'ubwubatsi, nk'iz'ibyumba by'umwuka bitagira ingufu, n'iz'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku kazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba badahari kubera uburwayi, kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya ko bashobora guhura n'abandi.
Ibicuruzwa bikenewe nuburyo bwo kubikura (urugero: kugura mugihe kitari cy'urugendo cyangwa kugura ukoresheje serivisi yo gutanga cyangwa gutwara (gura udakuye mu modoka), byombi birashobora guhindura uburyo bwubucuruzi.
Amaherezo, kohereza ibintu mu turere twihariye twibasiwe na COVID-19 bishobora kugira ingaruka. Gahunda yo kwitegura indwara zandura no kuyisubiza ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ingamba zo kwirinda.
Iyo gahunda igaragaza ibyago by'akazi n'aho umuntu akorera, hakubiyemo aho umuntu aturuka, aho atuye n'aho atuye, n'ibyago by'umuntu ku giti cye, urugero nk'imyaka y'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Bagaragaza uburyo bwo guhangana n'ibyo bibazo, n'uburyo bwo kwitegura uko icyorezo cyaguka.
Gutegura indwara zandura no kwitabira indwara zishobora kuba ari amabwiriza y'igihugu cyangwa y'akarere.
Intego zo gusubiza icyorezo harimo kugabanya ubwandu mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byo guhura n'ibibazo by'ubuzima, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku zindi nzego ziri mu mugabane w'ibicuruzwa byabo.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ubucuruzi buri, bugira ingaruka ku bisubizo by'abashakanye.
Gahunda yo kugenzura akaga ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu kugenzura umutekano w'akazi n'ubuzima.
Aho COVID-19 idashobora gukurwaho, ingamba z'ingirakamaro ni ingamba z'ubwubatsi, hanyuma iz'ubuyobozi, hanyuma n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubwubatsi bwerekeranye no kurinda abakozi ibyago byo gukora aho kwishingikiriza ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bishobora kuba igisubizo cyoroshye cyane cyo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Ingamba z'ubuyobozi ni ihinduka mu mahame cyangwa imikorere y'akazi, bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidakora neza kurusha ibyuma by'ubwubatsi n'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu gukumira ibyangijwe bimwe.
PPE igomba gutoranywa bitewe n'ibyago by'umukozi, ikagomba gufatwa neza (urugero nk'imiti yo guhumeka), ikagomba kwambarwa neza kandi neza, ikagenzurwa buri gihe, igakoreshwa neza kandi igasimbuzwa, kandi igatwikwa neza, igatunganywa neza kandi igatwarwa neza kugira ngo irinde kwangiza.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA) cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, akazi gafite ibyago bike byo guhura n'abantu, gafite ibikorwa bike cyane byo guhura n'abantu benshi ndetse n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura mu mirimo yose harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gutanga amabwiriza yo guhumeka harimo no gutwikira mu gihe cyo guhumeka no gukorora, gutanga ibikoresho byo gushyiraho imyanda, guhora witeguye gutumanaho cyangwa gukora amasaha atandukanye y'umunsi, kubuza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza gahunda yo gusukura no gukingira indwara mu gihe cy'akazi.
Ikintu cy'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abakandida n'abandi mu kazi, ni ukumenya vuba no gutandukanya abantu bashobora kwandura.
Abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitera inkunga yo kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe baruhutse umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro, n'ibindi bimenyetso by'indwara nibura amasaha 24 yose, nta miti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti ihindura ibimenyetso, kandi bagomba koroshya politiki y'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara, yemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kwita ku muntu urwaye wo mu muryango, kandi abakozi bagomba kumenya neza aya mahame.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, akazi gafite ibyago byo kwandura gashobora kuba ari akazi aho COVID-19 itazwi cyangwa ikekwa, ariko bisaba ko abantu bashobora kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2 bagirana imibonano mpuzabitsina idasanzwe cyangwa ya hafi mu kirere cya metero esheshatu (1.8m) bitewe n'uburwayi bukwirakwira mu baturage mu bigo by'ubucuruzi cyangwa se bitewe n'urugendo mpuzamahanga umuntu aherutse gukora mu gihugu aho COVID-19 yandukiye cyane.
Mu mabwiriza y'ubuyobozi agenga abakozi bafite gahunda yo guhura n'abantu benshi, harimo nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abantu benshi, n'ahandi hari amaduka ahari abantu benshi. Mu mabwiriza yo kubikoreramo no kubikoreramo agamije gufasha abantu bafite ibyago byinshi harimo gushyiraho ibirahuri by'umwuka bikora neza, kongera igipimo cy'umuyaga, gushyiraho inzitizi zikomeye nka za plastiki z'ubushyuhe, no gushyiraho idirishya ryo gutwara abantu ku kazi. Mu mabwiriza y'ubuyobozi agenga abakozi bafite ibyago byinshi harimo gutoza abarwayi kuguma mu ngo, gushyiraho ibikoresho by'ubwiru mu mwanya w'ibiro by'ubucuruzi, gushyiraho gahunda zitandukanye zo kwirinda COVID-19, guha abakozi amabwiriza yo kwirinda no kwirinda indwara z'uburwayi mu gihe cy'akazi, kwigisha abakozi ku bijyanye n'uko bakoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'ibanze cyangwa ibyangombwa by'ibanze, guhagarika ingendo, guhuza abantu ku kazi, no kubamenyesha abantu uko bakwirinda COVID-19 mu buryo bwihariye, no kubafasha guhangana n'ibizaza ku mirire cyangwa ibindi bibazo by'akazi.
Abakozi bari muri iri tsinda ry'ibyago bakenera gukoresha imashini zifasha guhumeka mu bihe bidasanzwe.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, ingamba zikwiye zo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bantu barimo gushyira abantu barwaye ku ntera ya metero 6 uvuye ku bandi, gushyiraho umukozi wo kwita ku barwayi, no guha umuntu urwaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa gusaba umuntu urwaye ko apfuka umunwa n'amavuta mu gihe asusumira cyangwa anuka.
Abakozi bo mu modoka bagombye kwambara udushumi tw'ubuvuzi dukoreshwa mu gihe basubiza umwenda w'umuntu urwaye cyangwa iyo bakorakora ku mazi yo mu mubiri cyangwa ahantu hashobora kwandura, kandi bashobora gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'umuntu ku giti cye mu gihe umurwayi afite umuriro, ubwonko cyangwa guhumeka.
Inkweto n'ibindi bintu bishobora kujugunywa bigomba kujugunywa mu mufuka w'ibinyabuzima, hanyuma ubutaka bwanduye bugakorwa isuku no gusukura. Ku mato y'ubucuruzi, harimo amato y'ubukwe n'andi mato y'abagenzi, ingamba zo kwirinda ibyago zirimo gusubika urugendo rw'uburwayi, kwigunga no guhita bamenyesha ikigo nderabuzima cyo mu bwato niba hari umuntu ufite umuriro cyangwa indi ndwara mu gihe ari mu bwato.
Mu buryo bwiza, umuntu wahawe ubwisungane mu kwivuza agomba gukurikiranwa mu cyumba cye. Ku bigo by'amashuri n'iby'uburezi, CDC isaba ko umuntu wahawe ubwisungane mu kwivuza yinjira mu kigo cy'ishuri mu gihe gito, kugira ngo akirindwe cyangwa akirandurwe, hatitawe ku cyorezo cy'ubwandu mu baturage.
Iyo indwara zidakwirakwira mu ruhame, uburyo bwo kwirinda abantu bashobora kubishyira mu bikorwa, nko guhagarika ingendo zo mu murima, amateraniro n'andi makoraniro manini, nko kwigisha umubiri cyangwa gusangira mu ishuri ry'umuziki cyangwa gufungurira mu kafeteri; kongera intera hagati y'amadesika, gutandukanya amasaha yo kuza mu biro n'amasaha y'ikiruhuko, kugabanya abantu bataba ngombwa, no gukoresha ahantu hiteganyirijwe abarwayi b'indwara z'ibicurane.
Mu gihe indwara zikwirakwira mu baturage, ingamba zo kwirinda kwitarura abandi zishobora guterwa no kongera igihe cyo guhagarika ishuri. CDC ivuga ko nta ngaruka ku buzima bw'abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora ibikorwa bya buri munsi.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba guhura n'abantu bafite COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho kuyirwara, bagirwa inama yo gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'ubutabazi b'ibiza, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Niba abakozi bahuye cyane mu gihe cy'ibyago, imyenda yabo n'ibikoresho byabo bigomba gusukurwa no gukoreshwa imiti yo guhanagura cyangwa kumesa hakoreshejwe umuti wo mu rugo mbere yo kongera gukoreshwa, kandi uburyo bwo gucunga ibimenyetso bugomba gukurikizwa mu kugenzura no guhagarika PPE yakoreshejwe.
OSHA isobanura ko abakozi bo mu nzego zimwe na zimwe z'ubuzima n'iz'urupfu bafite ibyago byinshi cyangwa byinshi byo guhura n'ibiyobyabwenge.
Imirimo y'ibyago byo guhura na COVID-19 ikubiyemo abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima, abashinzwe ubufasha, abakozi bo mu mavuriro n'abakora mu by'ubuvuzi, bahura n'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19.
Iyo abakozi bakora uburyo bwo gukora Aerosol, cyangwa bakusanya cyangwa bagakorana ibipimo by'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura na bo.
Uburyo bwo gukora Aerosol harimo gutwara umugozi, gutangiza ubuhumekero, bronchoscopy, uburyo bwo kuvura amenyo n'uburyo bwo gutwara ibipimo.
Imirimo y'ubushakashatsi y'ibyago byo guhura n'urupfu irimo abakozi bakora mu mirimo yo gutegura imibiri y'abantu bose bazwiho cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19 igihe bapfaga; iyo mirimo ishobora kuba ari yo ituma habaho ibyago byo guhura cyane mu gihe bakora autopsies. Ibindi byangombwa by'ubushakashatsi ku bantu bari muri iri tsinda ry'ibyago harimo amazu yo gutandukanya abarwayi bazwiho cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19, harimo n'aho bakorera ubu buryo bwo gukora Aerosol.
Kwinjiza umwuka mu buryo bwihariye butuma umuntu atagira umwuka mwiza bishobora gukoreshwa mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubuvuzi no mu byumba by'abarwayi.
Ibipimo bigomba gufatwa hakurikijwe ingamba zo kwirinda indwara zo mu rwego rwa 3 rw'ubwirinzi.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abarwayi bazahazwa mu byumba by'abategereje bibarirwa mu byiciro bitandukanye, hagendewe ku kuba bakekwaho COVID-19. OSHA yashyizeho uburyo bwo guhumeka, uretse PPE, ku bantu bakorera mu kirere kiri hagati y'ibirenge 6 by'abarwayi bazwiho cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite SARS-CoV-2.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, N95 yemewe na NIOSH cyangwa umuti wo guhumeka mu maso wa filtration wazamutse ugomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'ingamba zo kurinda ubuzima bw'umuntu, harimo n'amasomo, amahugurwa n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi.
Ubundi bwoko bw'ibinyabuzima bishobora gutanga uburinzi bwinshi kandi bigatuma abakozi barushaho kugira ihumure. WHO ntishishimiye ko umuntu yakwirakwiza covid-19, kuko COVID-19 idakwirakwizwa mu mazi yo mu mubiri, ahubwo ni indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
OMS isaba ko abakozi bakora ibizamini by'ubuvuzi bambara agapfukamunwa gusa iyo bageze ku kibuga.
OMS isaba ko abantu bakusanya, bakita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa bakabatwara mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero nta buryo bwo gukora Aerosol, bakambara udupfukamunwa, indorerwamo, cyangwa indorerwamo.
Iyo habonetse uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, icyo gikoresho cy'ubuvuzi gishyirwamo N95 cyangwa FFP2 respirator.
Kubera ko ku isi hose PPE idahabwa abantu benshi, OMS irasaba ko hakoreshwa imiti ya terefone, ko hakoreshwa intera hagati y'abantu, nko gukoresha amadirishya asukuye, ko hakoreshwa abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu gihe umuntu ari mu cyumba, ko hakoreshwa PPE ikenewe gusa, ko hakoreshwa ibikoresho byo mu rwego rwo guhumeka mu gihe umuntu ari mu cyiciro kimwe, ko hakoreshwa ibikoresho byo guhumeka mu gihe umuntu ari mu cyiciro kimwe, ko hakoreshwa uburyo bwo kugenzura no guhuza imikorere y'itangwa rya PPE, kandi ko abantu badafite ibimenyetso bakwiriye guhora bambaye agapfukamunwa.
