Indwara ziterwa na koronavirusi, ni ubwoko bw'indwara zifitanye isano rya bugufi
Li Wenliang, umuganga mu bitaro bya Wuhan Central Hospital, yishwe na COVID-19 nyuma yo gukangurira abantu kumenya ko virusi ikwirakwira.
